				<wikidot:authorName>EndgamerAzari</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1039831</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm loving the varied tones/motivations of the various Misters. Mr. Redd is going to have one hell of a strange encounter when they all catch up to him.</p> <p>Possibly one of the most disturbing things about Mr. Stripes is the way he subtly contradicts himself&#8212;he keeps jumping between the past and present tense when describing himself. Makes me wonder if he's just deranged or there's actually something to it.</p> 
				 	]]>
